Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.20,0:22:44.08,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}滲透著濃濃的溫情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.37,0:22:49.59,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}直到你入睡為止
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.80,0:22:55.04,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}將我笨拙的愛傳遞給你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.13,0:23:00.78,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}無論是傷心還是歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.86,0:23:06.03,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}從遭遇悲痛的那天起  我就變得不再是我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.10,0:23:08.83,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}就像某人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.91,0:23:11.79,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}無法好好地生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.90,0:23:14.73,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}若是還能再相見
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.80,0:23:19.81,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}想把心中的一切都
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.92,0:23:23.74,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\blur4}告訴你
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,TXT
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.40,0:00:07.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉讓你陪我到這麼晚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.34,0:00:10.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有女孩子在房間裡等你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.40,0:00:12.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,之前已經告訴過她會晚回來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.97,0:00:15.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都這時候了應該沒在等了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.13,0:00:18.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再見  JB
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.87,0:00:20.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下  雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.89,0:00:21.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.75,0:00:26.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安  雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.46,0:00:32.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她搞什麼鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.17,0:00:34.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.33,0:00:39.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個我…什麼都沒看見
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.52,0:00:42.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  你一定產生了很大的誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.02,0:00:44.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聽我解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.17,0:00:45.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.69,0:00:47.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是大人之間的玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.53,0:00:50.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧  我不會和其他人說的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.17,0:00:52.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別看我這樣  其實口風很緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.20,0:00:53.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不信的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.00,0:00:56.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你要立刻推倒我  強吻一下看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.62,0:01:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,風見先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.70,0:01:01.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.72,0:01:06.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說我接下來會被強暴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.36,0:01:07.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.51,0:01:09.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夠了  回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:12.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.14,0:01:16.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.56,0:02:51.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:53.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你還在等我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.94,0:02:56.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧  正好也有事情要做
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.77,0:02:58.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幫你燙好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.38,0:03:01.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有你的鈕釦鬆了  幫你縫好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.68,0:03:03.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.39,0:03:05.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在要吃飯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.11,0:03:07.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還是要先洗個澡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.11,0:03:11.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,或者說想要…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.47,0:03:12.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我先洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.05,0:03:21.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吶  天音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:24.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要為我做到這種地步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.19,0:03:27.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了  對你一見鐘情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.34,0:03:30.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能夠接受這樣的解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.65,0:03:32.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,理由太過隨便了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.63,0:03:34.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是雄二你不知道而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.48,0:03:37.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算有我這樣子的女孩也不奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.25,0:03:40.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  讓你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:41.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.42,0:03:45.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  郵件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.02,0:03:48.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是小幸發來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.31,0:03:49.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.44,0:03:52.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吶  雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.86,0:03:55.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.19,0:03:57.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs32\fad(0,500)}From  小幸\NTo       周防天音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.19,0:03:57.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs32\fad(0,500)}主題   我什麼都沒有說\N然後我什麼都沒看到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.97,0:04:00.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…對了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.48,0:04:02.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你之前也見過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.41,0:04:05.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她叫JB  是我的上司
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.13,0:04:06.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,上司？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.40,0:04:08.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  這是她的惡作劇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.53,0:04:11.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.53,0:04:12.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你什麼都不問嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.02,0:04:16.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你不是討厭別人過問你的工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.33,0:04:18.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還是說你希望我去懷疑什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.09,0:04:20.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.49,0:04:24.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道雄二你想讓我吃醋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.50,0:04:27.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  沒這打算
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.42,0:04:32.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就吃下醋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.39,0:04:34.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.25,0:04:36.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來個吻的話  也許就原諒你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.48,0:04:39.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這女人  到底哪句真哪句假
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.41,0:04:42.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,或者說  她到底有多小看男人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.27,0:04:44.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.70,0:04:48.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  閉上眼吧  天音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.34,0:04:52.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真強硬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.30,0:04:53.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.51,0:05:20.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…  可是第一次接吻啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.04,0:05:23.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真巧  其實我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.41,0:05:26.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,騙子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.17,0:05:30.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺雄二的吻已經相當熟練了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.95,0:05:32.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  我下次會注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.23,0:05:36.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這話是代表還有下次嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.24,0:05:37.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是說說而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.24,0:05:42.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛  親我原來只是玩玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.01,0:05:45.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別說得這麼難聽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.16,0:05:49.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不是沒有任何覺悟就做這種粗暴的行為的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.51,0:05:50.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.02,0:05:53.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你迷上我是你的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.64,0:05:54.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就認可了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.02,0:05:59.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我不能保證一生都能照顧你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.73,0:06:03.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說  你承認我是你的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.12,0:06:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但你無法成為我的男朋友這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.22,0:06:07.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.39,0:06:10.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.38,0:06:14.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,結論就是我可以成為你的女朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.38,0:06:17.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  但是有一個條件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.29,0:06:20.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我突然消失  或者突然死去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.63,0:06:21.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不要哭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.53,0:06:26.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後在一年內  努力把我忘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:28.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接受這些條件的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:30.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就可以成為你的女朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.55,0:06:33.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.35,0:06:36.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我接受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:40.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作為交換  雄二你喜歡我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.87,0:06:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個希望你能現在就告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.56,0:06:48.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我對這方面的感情不太懂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在對你的感情究竟是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.54,0:06:54.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.03,0:06:56.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.31,0:07:00.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  能聽到你這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.99,0:07:04.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我現在就是雄二的女朋友了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:05.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.15,0:07:07.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.63,0:07:10.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.92,0:07:11.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.90,0:07:14.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,突然一下子沒力氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.48,0:07:16.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,膝蓋不停地顫抖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.01,0:07:20.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然很開心  卻沒有什麼實感
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.55,0:07:27.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  我是雄二的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.32,0:07:29.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺好噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.99,0:07:31.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,站起來吧  來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.10,0:07:34.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要讓我站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.34,0:07:36.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的我可是無法反抗的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.41,0:07:38.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你想說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.71,0:07:43.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說  我在提示你現在可以把我上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.83,0:07:45.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.08,0:07:48.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣  要做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.11,0:07:50.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會非常舒服的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:57.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛啊  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.10,0:07:58.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明全身都在顫抖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.94,0:08:00.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就別得意了吧  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.19,0:08:04.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.16,0:08:06.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,的確我沒有和女生交往過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.29,0:08:09.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  正因為如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.54,0:08:12.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我才想知道你為何如此想和我交往
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.63,0:08:16.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了是一見鐘情…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.39,0:08:18.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.65,0:08:23.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.39,0:08:26.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴我  你這麼做的原因是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.58,0:08:39.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,私立瀧園學園1年A班
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.28,0:08:44.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,籃球社成員  風見一姬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.75,0:08:47.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你肯定認識吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.58,0:08:51.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼認不認識  她是我姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.67,0:08:52.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.71,0:08:57.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,6年前的8月14日  女子籃球社
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.92,0:09:00.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在夏季合宿的回程路上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.91,0:09:05.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,包括她在內14人搭乘的小巴失去了蹤跡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.94,0:09:08.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「瀧園學園小巴墜崖事故」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.22,0:09:12.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是那個事故中的唯一生還者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.78,0:09:18.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你的姐姐是同級生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.00,0:09:21.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼這麼重要的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.40,0:09:25.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  我說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.89,0:09:27.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你剛轉學過來的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:29.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就馬上發覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.73,0:09:30.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.16,0:09:36.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等我一下  雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.60,0:09:40.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我有東西要給你看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.33,0:09:46.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是那天的日記
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.96,0:09:49.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,裡面記載了所有的經過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.06,0:09:50.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.91,0:10:01.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,6年前的8月14日…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.63,0:10:06.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們結束了夏季合宿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.97,0:10:08.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在回去學校的路上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.30,0:10:11.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老師  是這條路沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.88,0:10:12.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.78,0:10:18.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.73,0:10:19.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小阿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.90,0:10:20.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,安全帶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.21,0:10:24.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.01,0:10:45.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.13,0:10:47.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,醒過來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.73,0:10:50.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼能麻煩你從我身上移開嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.61,0:10:52.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.58,0:10:55.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛啊  移動的時候小心一點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.68,0:10:57.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.72,0:11:01.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我之後會去揍你的  告訴我你名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:03.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:07.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我開玩笑的  我叫風見一姬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.66,0:11:08.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.05,0:11:11.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫周防  周防天音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.86,0:11:15.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,周防同學嗎  雖然知道名字和相貌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.12,0:11:16.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過和你說話是第一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.38,0:11:19.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.25,0:11:22.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敬語就免了  我和你都是一年級生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.13,0:11:26.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有  如果可以的話  能麻煩你趕緊從我身上下來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.23,0:11:28.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:29.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第四次了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.47,0:11:30.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.54,0:11:34.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「對不起」這句話  說得越多就越不值錢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.04,0:11:36.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再說的話  我可要生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.95,0:11:42.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  從左邊離開  出口在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.75,0:11:43.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.04,0:11:50.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總算是逃出生天了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.14,0:11:52.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給  這是你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.87,0:11:56.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  嗯  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.96,0:12:03.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼  有問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:04.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.90,0:12:08.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來  我們該先去救誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:10.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.74,0:12:12.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,二  你的好友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.83,0:12:14.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三  受傷的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.70,0:12:16.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你選的話你會先救誰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.44,0:12:20.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,風見同學想先救誰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.62,0:12:24.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對提問人進行反問是很蠢的行為
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.60,0:12:27.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別再幹這種事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.96,0:12:30.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  那先救部長吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.78,0:12:31.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.86,0:12:34.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我討厭她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.22,0:12:34.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.14,0:12:36.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那問題的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.54,0:12:39.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我選四  先救我討厭的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.26,0:12:42.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,選四  你這是賴皮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.62,0:12:46.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,選項裡面沒有正確答案時你會怎麼回答
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.34,0:12:48.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也包含在這個心理測試裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.36,0:12:50.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要先救自己討厭的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.06,0:12:53.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡可是有12個人要救
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.81,0:12:55.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是自己討厭的人留到最後再救
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:59.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定會感到厭煩的吧
